// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3037 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c49c3c4d-5c01-5f06-8110-fc31184a365d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
